Map {
Computer Hardware Application {
    User Story 1: As a user, I want to be able to view all orders that are not supported by the application.
    User Story 2: As a user, I want to be able to select the travel time for my order.
    User Story 3: As a user, I want to be able to view the status of my order.
    User Story 4: As a user, I want to be able to view the estimated delivery time for my order.
    User Story 5: As a user, I want to be able to view the cost of my order.
    User Story 6: As a user, I want to be able to view the warranty information for my order.
    User Story 7: As a user, I want to be able to view the technical specifications for my order.
    User Story 8: As a user, I want to be able to view the compatibility of my order with other hardware.
    User Story 9: As a user, I want to be able to view the return policy for my order.
    User Story 10: As a user, I want to be able to view the customer service contact information for my order.
}
}
